    "preserve": "Never translate or alter — always output verbatim in both locales.",
    "preferred": "A standardized translation to use — flags any other rendering of the source term.",
    "forbidden": "A term or translation that must never appear in published content.",
    "contextual": "Documented variation is allowed depending on context — informational only, never blocks the gate."
